accomplishment_projects.title: Kit Cosmos platform
accomplishment_projects.description:
Enterprise scale platform for managing and delivery of the video content. Supporting full range on user devices (PC, Tables, Smartphones, set-top boxes, game consoles and so on). Platform integrated with digital right management system, CDN, video transcoding and ingestion module, billing, and number of the other components.
I was working on VoD Portal which it the most complex and loaded part as it handles thousands of users, contains main business logic of the system and integrated with all other sub-systems which we use. Also I was involved in indexing service implementation based on Solr engine and Customer Care portal development which is complex java script appliacation build via ExtJS framework.

Technologies: java 7, Spring Framework, Freemarker, JAX-WS/JAX-RS services, Maven, Oracle, ExtJS, Silverlight, MongoDB, Linux, jQuery, Hibernate, Solr

accomplishment_projects.title: NGP (New Generation Platform)
accomplishment_projects.description:
Video content management system: video asset ingestion and transcoding, publishing, billing, building schedules for broadcasting, publishing EPGs. This new platform was targeted to replace number of legacy projects as part of KIT Cosmos platform.
I was involved as back-end developer, presentation tier was implemented in Abode Flex by UX team. My main commitments was implementation of complex persistence framework which allows to extend base domain entities with custom configurable properties, EPG ingestion via biztalk workflow, also I developed kind of domain specific language which allows to automate video ingestion process and content matching engine which allows to generate dynamic playlists by configurable criteria.

Technologies: .Net, C# 4, WCF 4, SOA, Fluent-NHibernate, MS SQL, Biztalk
